{"tid":1472101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"818 和理非 仲出唔出嚟好？","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:18:01.000Z","uid":221069,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04cd41e0bee85df25bd4a6cb4114d70ed6cea5ef","tid":1472101,"uid":221069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得紀律部隊情緒失控係可以接受，你應該理解臥底對平民示威者帶來的心理影響；相反<br />\n如果你反對警察選擇性執法、濫暴、私刑，麻煩你唔好試圖用歪理去掩飾尋晚嘅暴行<br />\n<br />\n理解唔等於認同<br />\n認錯唔等於割蓆<br />\n反省唔等於分化<br />\n<br />\n唔係要做道德L，只係唔好嚴人寬己，如果唔係你就同班黑警一L樣<br />\n<br />\n我係和理非，8 18 仲應唔應該出嚟？<br />\n<br />\n由 day 1 開始都已經講無大台，你想要嘅嘢未回應咪出囉。前線打交關你叉事，你唔認同咪唔好打，唔好上前線囉。除咗政府過往果廿年施政之外，成個運動無人迫過你出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n琴晚嘅事正正反映咗人係唔完美嘅。<br />\n無論你幾有理想，政治理念有幾崇高，你都係一個人，一個同黑警一樣有情緒，會犯錯嘅人。分別在於你會受法律制裁，佢唔會，所以係未爭取返一個公平、公正嘅制度之前，唔好放棄。<br />\n<br />\n未來勇武應該點？<br />\n我唔係勇武，無資格講。<br />\n只希望你地行動前，停一停，諗一諗<br />\n記住我地嘅目標係政府，係制度。<br />\n制度完善咗，黑警、狗官自然有法律制裁。<br />\n淨係將怒火發洩係警察和非同路人身上係唔會得到任何回報。請三思。"},{"pid":"a2623e28573cc8edecf4a49cf65a0810488601c9","tid":1472101,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1142b1b4be8bba56648fc8369edb8adf23a557d0","tid":1472101,"uid":221069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"150ee85381d06ee70d9d8b8cb3b78247262d361b","tid":1472101,"uid":286135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"818 一個都不能少"},{"pid":"82f593f189d086ee3bb940468b561ef35b684b56","tid":1472101,"uid":221069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:38:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9670b2fbd1419b03bf21201b0c7d476fd90f586b","tid":1472101,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"go"},{"pid":"68d9b8a690297026bc104e3e43e301cded0bfda3","tid":1472101,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;無大台的下一步! 無符號(semiotics)!&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464335\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464335</a>"},{"pid":"6bbef276803687385d87faffefe3ed5dc1e67cab","tid":1472101,"uid":164060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:41:00.000Z","msg":"推 有少少建議 所有poster都加返遊行info<br />\n時間 日期 開始地點 路線 方便大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" clas